name: Namrita
review: Great place to stay, easy check in & check out with host, kitchen was very well stocked and place was very clean and cozy!

name: Kimiye
review: Beautiful stay. My grandparents stayed in this suite for their week long vacation. They really loved it. Super clean, with everything you would need and more. Antonio gave them his phone number in case which is wonderful. Thank you!!

name: Kawssar
review: Great place, very well located only a few minutes away from a bus stop

name: Marilyn
review: This place was amazing, clean and in a great location! Would definitely recommend staying here!

name: Abed
review: Antonio and Lilly are fantastic hosts - so friendly and welcoming. We felt right at home staying there, and the suite is very nice and well equipped with its modern finishings. A wonderful stay!
